          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Admin-10mm-Step-1-1618232487722-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Slice your <strong>halloumi</strong> into thin strips</p><p>Top, tail and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong>,<strong> </strong>then add to a bowl with your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled carrot</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1584988252049-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1584988252049-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1584988252049-x700.jpg",
