            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel the <strong>remaining</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>orange</strong> and slice into segments</p><p>Chop your <strong>dill</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Remove the base of your <strong>lettuce</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred roughly</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
